{
  "stem": "17337.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "In other words, we got a soup at night in the-- in the camp, and then during the lunchtime because a lot of Poles used to work in that factory too.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And that's how we built.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I was-- I was tall and skinny, so I was chosen by a-- by a German.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You know, by the way, the factory was built by a private company by the name [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That's the biggest German company in Germany now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was chosen to work together with a German to put down the windows.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they were especially heavy, heavy windows with screws, not-- not [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I worked with him, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and we used to work for-- for until we finished that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was almost finished, the factory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was around the end of 1944.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the Russians were closing up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the factory was never finished.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then we started to take apart the factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as we were in the-- in the barracks-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Now, in between, half of the camp was sent out to Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Half of the people working with Schindler--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Half of the people-- not only from Schindler, there used to be another-- another factory there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the people used to work there, you know, not only by Schindler, but they used to work in another factory.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were sent out to Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was the one who was left over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I stayed there still.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were at a-- we had a very cramped barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, there was a lot people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, we sleep two in one bed because they didn't have enough room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when they left, they transported us to this-- to the other barracks.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
